description:
On today’s show, Emily is revealing the common lies that people tell around sex – which we’re all guilty of telling at least one. Plus, she’s taking your calls.

She discusses the lies men and women tell around sex – and why it’s better to just be honest. Then, she gives advice on what to do when you’ve tried to be sexually compatible, but it just doesn’t seem possible, tips on swallowing without gagging – with one you may not have heard, and how to love your body when you’ve got some asymmetrical anatomy going on.
